{"title":"天马歌","authors":["邹荻帆"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":1,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"天马歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邹荻帆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一群天马行太空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞越关山千万重。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滚滚风云马蹄急，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昂首一声天地红。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天马就是总路线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一飞冲天跃进中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"超额指标揭金榜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利的焰火怎不喷满我心胸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢铁超额完成指标抛红线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一马当先跨过1962年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粮食快马挥鞭胜灾害，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"煤棉猛冲猛打又占先……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"聚宝藏珠处处是，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"堆金积玉时时传，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摇醒穷山取金矿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大战荒旱变丰年……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领袖思想昭日月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的领导乾坤旋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肝胆相照志成城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手脑并勤定胜天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1959年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1959年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工业体系布下钢铁阵："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大烟囱吹向稻麦田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小机床响在茅棚间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男女老少都动手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大中小型齐冒烟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1959年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1959年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社基层织锦绣："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农林牧副渔一齐搞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工农商学兵总动员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动热情结硕果，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"技术革新花朵鲜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1960年，前进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1960年，向前！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工厂烟柱合唱列阵容，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灌溉系统乐谱颂大同，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以钢为纲最强音，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一亩一猪粮食丰……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一群天马行太空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞越关山千万重。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滚滚风云马蹄急，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昂首一声天地红。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新年又有新跃进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一飞冲天跃进中。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日日月月揭金榜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时时谱唱满堂红。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工农业交响乐民族风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指挥就是领袖毛泽东。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"号令一出山河改，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一群天马行太空……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}